Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miss Cheerilee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you brought\Nyour thinking caps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because today we're going\Nto learn about physics!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Physics?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm. Specifically, the use of\Nforce in energy conversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, using mechanical\Nwork to convert potential energy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,into kinetic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The what, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Mrs. Cheerilee, that\Nsounds a bit over our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Why would we even\Nneed to know that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you'll most likely\Nend up using it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, for participating in the ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,APPLEWOOD DERBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, WHEW! For a second I\Nthought we were gonna have to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... learn stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NDerpy is Best Muffin!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.no/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to race in the Applewood\NDerby tomorrow? That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My family's talked\Nabout it for years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I'm finally\Nold enough to race!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold onto your\Nhorseshoes, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of work to do\Nbefore you're ready to race.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but not\Nschool work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be a block of\Napplewood just like this one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for you at Sweet\NApple Acres tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've got one day to turn\Nit into a race-ready cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Awwwwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That is\Na lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Luckily, you'll each\Nget to pick an older pony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to help you. But\Nchoose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because they'll also\Nhave to ride in the cart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with you during the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I think I know\Njust the pony to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember everypony,\Nyour cart has to be able
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to finish the race if you want\Nto win one of the awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fastest, for winning\Nthe race, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Most Traditional, for\Nthe best working replica
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of an original Applewood cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And Most Creative, for the cart\Nwith the best overall design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-eee! Those ribbons\Nare the bees' knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, class.\NYou've got a lot to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to\Nbuild a race cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I knew there was\Ngonna be a catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, have you seen what the\Ncarts used to look like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the olden days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I know all about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When Ponyville\Nstarted the derby,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they decided to\Nuse the wood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from our apple trees\Nfor the carts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The race has been a part of\NSweet Apple Acres ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think these old\Ncarts look so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess you and Applejack\Nwill probably win the award
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for most traditional, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Apples usually\Ndo, but honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather build the fastest\Ncart there is and win the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty sure\NScoot and Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,will take that award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I race around\Nso much on my scooter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,being the fastest isn't such\Na big deal. Maybe I'll try
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the wildest-looking\Ncart I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. If I win\NMost Creative,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can totally win\Nthe award for Fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can win the award\Nfor Most Traditional!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like we're all going\Nto try something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to\Ntell Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,GOOOOO CRUSADERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding! Of course I'll\Nhelp with the Applewood Derby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to have as much fun\Nas I did when I was a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Cloudsdale\Nhas a derby too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Practically every\Ntown in Equestria has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember\Nracing my cloud cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS. IS. SO. AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,WHOOHOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And let me guess...\NYou won Fastest Cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you say? Will you\Nhelp me make my race cart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help you? I'm ALL OVER IT.\NI've got tons of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've got a\Nlot of ideas of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprint for my\NDerby cart, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to change it a little\Ncause this race is on roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,not on clouds, but trust me,\Nyour cart is gonna be AMAZING!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, OK, Rainbow Dash, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How awesome is THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With Dash on my team, how\Ncould anything go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, well I'm mighty\Nflattered you wanna work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with your big sis on your cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the "Applewood\NDerby" did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...start on our farm. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't be more proud\Nto help my little sister
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,take the prize for\N"Most Traditional!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I was kinda thinkin' of\Nsomethin' else. Like fastest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fastest?" Apple Bloom,\Nthings aren't like they were
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The fastest cart now has gotta\Nbe slick and modern and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...not Apple at all. The\NApples win Most Traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have since the Derby started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would anypony want\Nto win anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you head off\Nand get some chamomile vines,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,some hickory sticks,\Nand some apple barrels
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll show you what an Apple\NFamily cart should look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I do have a family\Ntradition to uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,THE APPLEWOOD DERBY?\NOf course I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, uh, Rarity, I didn't\Nknow you'd be this excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Oh why, I'm just itching\Nto right an old wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,from long, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I designed my own cart\Nwhen I was just a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was positive I was\Ngoing to win the prize for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Most Creative," hooves down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I came in second. Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You? Second for Most\NCreative? To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I learned a valuable lesson.\NI learned to know my audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the race cart audience\Nwants big! They want bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop, chop, everypony\Nout! We've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This will take all of\Nmy considerable skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will fashion the biggest\Nand boldest derby cart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to ever win the prize\Nfor Most Creative!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was sort of\Nthinking of something more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ha ha! Oh please, darling,\Nleave tradition to the Apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing big and bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon the prize for Most Creative\Nwill finally be in my hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean MY hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what I\Nsaid "my hooves."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, I hope you're ready to\Nget an early start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, how early?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, the sun's not even up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Apples, quit complaining. In\Nmy day, we were up even earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'd get up in the\Nmiddle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,if it means my cart crosses\Nthat finish line first
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and wins Fastest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And my cart wins Most Creative!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And my cart wins\NMost Traditional!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-eee!, it's\Ngonna be a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean "our" carts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that what we said, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our carts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Their" carts? It almost\Nsounds like they're planning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,on building them without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they meant "our" carts,\Nlike the team cart. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I mean they're\Nall our older sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,practically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus they've all done this\Nbefore. I'm sure they know best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just buckle\Ndown and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo,\Nwhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only got till noon to\Nmake the fastest cart ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really thinking of going\Nfor the Most Creative prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know all about\Nspeed already so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! It's all about speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta get across the\Nfinish line to win a prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so we might as well\Nget there first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I left a bunch of\Npaint cans by the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them up here, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing as fun as\Npainting racing stripes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,on the winning cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spendin' time building a\Ncart with my big sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,why this is just tee-riffic!\NUm, how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feast your\Neyes on... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it ain't\Nquite finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't it have the makings of\Nthe best cart you ever did see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, is somethin'\Nwrong, Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was kinda\Nthinking of something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a little more modern.\NAnd less rickety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With maybe a chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless my hooves, I\Nthought we covered this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tradition is all that counts\Nand who knows tradition better
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,than Apples? Nopony! That's who!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you an Apple\Nor are you an Apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an Apple. But, what if I\Njust take off this fringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,NO! NOT THE FRINGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, shoot, now I've gotta\Nstart all over from scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's almost race time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So maybe we can redesign\Nit then... just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No time! And who'd want\Nto redesign something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that's already perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so I sketched\Nout some of my ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a nice\Nyellow fringe on top?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho, darling, the\Nfringe is not exactly big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that yellow is the least\Nbold color I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't\Nhave to be yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really do love the\Nold-timey style. Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, precious face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Old-Timey" is just\Nanother word for passé!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, BIG and BOLD! I do\Nhave a reputation to uphold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one thing\Nto lose as a filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but can you imagine if I didn't\Nwin the Most Creative now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies might stop\Nbuying my couture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're supposed to\Nbe doing this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course we are, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we just\Nfinished! Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You're speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that isn't big and\Nbold, I don't know what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Crusader.\NHow's it goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity's definitely made\Nthe biggest, boldest cart
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,anypony's ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Well, Applejack's built\Nsomething so traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's practically an antique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say, there's\Nno talking Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,out of making the fastest\Ncart in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like any of us\Nended up with what we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure our older sisters\Nknow what they're doing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if our carts aren't\Nexactly what we had in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll still be fun to drive\Nthem to the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. The race is\Nthe best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. CMCs behind the wheels!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Derby Racers, to\Nthe starting line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Derby Racers, to\Nthe starting line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The race is about\Nto start, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You better shake a leg if you\Nwant a ride in the winning cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Sweetie Belle. There's\Nonly one seat left aboard
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this creative masterpiece and\Nit's just for you. Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, ponies! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This traditional cart handles at\Nthe exact perfect pace. Slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got the passenger seat all\Nwarmed up for you, Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Passenger seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. They're the only\Nolder ponies driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,First they built the carts;\Nnow they're gonna drive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they were\Nall excited to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think they're\Nreally helping any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We better hurry if we want to\Nbe a part of this race at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, aren't you all\Nmissing somepony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh, usually the younger\Nponies drive the carts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, do these look\Nlike "usual" carts to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Racers, on your marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get set... GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAHHH... can't\Nwe go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster? Don't be\Nsilly; this is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ GO GO GO! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Check me out: racin' the{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Check out my old-fashioned{\i0}\N{\i1} cart! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Check me out: racing{\i0}\N{\i1} the Derby ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ in my original work of art! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Check me out:{\i0}\N{\i1} faster than ever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} There's nopony can{\i0}\N{\i1} catch me now! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Let me out! I'd do it over ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ if I only knew how! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby Racers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1}Derby Racers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby Racers ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ GO GO GO! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ My cart's the most original! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Designed with imagination. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My cart's the most{\i0}\N{\i1} traditional! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Just plain no complications. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Look at me I am the Ace! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Might as well give{\i0}\N{\i1} up the chase. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Wish we could stop this race,{\i0}\N{\i1}start again and do it our way. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Having any fun yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Nope! Maybe if we could{\i0}\N{\i1} go a little faster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1}Derby Racers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby Racers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby Racers ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ GO GO GO! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Gotta get some attention{\i0}\N{\i1} if I want that ribbon! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Gotta push the limits further,{\i0}\N{\i1} blow away the competition! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Gotta coast on through, just{\i0}\N{\i1} relax we're gonna cruise it. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Guess I don't really care ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ since we're clearly{\i0}\N{\i1} gonna lose it. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ See everypony's watching,{\i0}\N{\i1} presentation is our glory. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just passed you even faster,{\i0}\N{\i1} speed is king end of story! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Bigger, Bolder{\i0}\N{\i1} down the track ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Love the view from{\i0}\N{\i1} the back of the pack. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Won't stop, we're{\i0}\N{\i1} on the attack! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Too late to take it{\i0}\N{\i1} all back! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby Racers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1}Derby Racers! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Giddy-up,{\i0}\N{\i1} Derby Racers ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ GO GO ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,LOOK OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! My beautiful swan\Ncart is an ugly duckling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And my old time cart is\Na rootin'-tootin' wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It still counts as a win if I\Npush my cart across, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE NOT YOUR CARTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed\Nto design them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were supposed\Nto drive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Derby was supposed to be\Nfor us, not the three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've ruined\Nit for everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, I suppose\Nwe might have gotten
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a teensy bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you\Nall wanted our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We did. We wanted your\Nhelp to build our carts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but we all ended\Nup with carts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that are what each\Nof you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't\Nyou say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all done the race before.\NI just figured you knew best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus it's hard to speak\Nup to older ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I certainly\Nunderstand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but you mustn't think older\Nponies automatically know best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And we probably could\Nhave done a better job
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we owe all\Nthree of you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. How do you feel\Nabout a do over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a\Nwonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe the older ponies\Nshould sit this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping us fix up our\Ncarts. Pretty creative, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not traditional, but\Nit sure looks fast, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, darling, I can't\Nbelieve I'm saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but that yellow fringe\Nis rather bold after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everypony! We couldn't\Nhave done it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I sure am glad\NMs. Cheerilee agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to run the race over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't every year I\Nget to say this twice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Derby Racers, to\Nthe starting line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Derby Racers, to\Nthe starting line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Racers, on your\Nmarks, get set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's probably best\Nkeeping all the grownups
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,on the sidelines, but what\Nare we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Much better. Honestly,\NI'm not sure why we wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to race those carts\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously! This is the most\Nrelaxed I've been all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,GO SCOOTALOO! GO!\NWHOO-WHOO-WHOO-WHOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I mean... this is the\Nlife. Right, ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
